Package handlers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthorizingRequestHandler
    Base class for requests that require an auth token to perform the request.
    ClearHandler
    Handlers requests to clear all data from the database
    EventHandler
    Handles requests to get event data from the database
    FileHandler
    This class handles any request that is not implemented by another handler and interprets it as a request for a file to be displayed.
    FillHandler
    Handles requests to generate a specified number of generations of person and event data for a given user
    LoadHandler
    Handles request to load data into the database
    LoginHandler
    Handles requests to login a user that has been registered in the database and returns a new auth token.
    PersonHandler
    Handles requests to get person data from the database
    PostRequestHandler
    Base class for Handlers that handle a post request.
    RegisterHandler
    Handles requests to register a new user to the database and returns a new auth token.
    RequestHandler
    This class implements the base functionality of each of the server's handlers.
